Barely a month after purchasing two brand new luxurious automobiles, actress Laide Bakare has acquired a third. Excited Laide took to her Instagram page to flaunt her new car as she shared photos of the silver-coloured Mercedes Benz. She posed in front of the Benz alone and with her kids. Attributing her successes to adequate preparation, hard work and learning from failure, the 41-year-old movie star told off critics who would allege she slept her way to the feat.   Naira Marley releases debut album “God’s…     Stop shaving your public hairs, Blessing CEO advises ladies     Five most educated Nigerian celebrities   She wrote: “My BOOK, HOW TO GET SUPER RICH IN 6 MONTH IS COMING SOON. How can you call it show off when I haven’t even told you I just got this NEW Benz last week. “There is no secret to my success, it’s the result of PREPARATIONS, HARD WORK AND learning from my failure. MANY EFFORTS MUCH PROSPERITY. “I REPEAT my sweat, MY MONEY, my Reward, my pride, my home my happiness. “If you think p**zy can get you all these Achievements haaa!!! omo!!! The Area go just expand in vein ni o so stop lying to the public, ME ke? ME wey be say, NA paiko I dey even presently I DO NOT HAVE A BOYFRIEND, My focus is majorly on my Business and my children.” On May 3, few weeks after Laide Bakare opened her new mansion in Lekki- Lagos, she acquired two new exotic cars, a black Toyota and a white Lexus.